; Regression test for issue #622: print changes Y.... tag to YYYY/MM/DD day - should preserve Y.... tag (BZ#622)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/622
; The Y YYYY directive sets a default year for short-form dates.
; When print is run, the Y directive is dropped and dates are expanded
; to full YYYY/MM/DD format rather than preserving the Y directive.

Y 2013

01/01 Payee
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test print
2013/01/01 Payee
    Expenses:Food                             $10.00
    Assets:Cash
end test
